{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"他们互相询问，询问什么"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"询问那重大的消息，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"就是他们所争论的消息。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"绝不然!他们将来就知道 了。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"绝不然，他们将来就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"难道我没有使 大地如摇篮，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"使山峦如木桩吗"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我曾把你们造成配 偶，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"我曾使你们从睡眠中得到休息，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"我曾以黑夜为 帷幕，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"我曾以白昼供谋生，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"我曾在你们上面建造 了七层坚固的天，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"我曾创造一盏明灯，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"我从含水 的云里，降下滂沱大雨，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"以便我借它而生出百谷和草 木，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"以及茂密的园圃。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"判决之日，确是指定的日 期，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"在那日，号角将被吹响，你们就成群而来；"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"天 将被开辟，有许多门户"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"山峦将被移动，而变成幻影"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"火狱确是伺候着，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"作悖逆者的归宿"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"他们将在 其中逗留长久的时期。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他们在其中不能睡眠，不得饮 料，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"只饮沸水和脓汁。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"那是一个很相当的报酬。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"他们的确不怕清算，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他们曾否认我的迹象，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"我曾 将万事记录在一本天经里。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"(将对他们说:)“你们尝试 吧!我只增加你们所受的刑罚。”"}]}